headline.main: Wanted: Female Candidates for Algeria's Parliament Quota
headline.print_headline: Wanted: Female Candidates for Algeria's Parliament Quota

lead_paragraph: Algerian law requires the next parliament to be made up of 30 percent women — but political parties across the spectrum have struggled to come up with enough female candidates to fill the quota.
